episodes.title: S4 Episode 22- #DancingWithTheDevil
episodes.description: In today's episode, most of the gang sit down to discuss the documentary series "Dancing with the Devil." They talk about cults in general and the 7M management company, run by a guy who manipulated young dancers. How did he do it? How did the dancers get involved? They also talk about the music that was popular back in the day, and how it shaped the way we think about the world. episodes.title: S4 Episode 3 - #Cults
episodes.description: In this episode, Jamaine and Kathryn discuss the rise of cults in America and the polarized nature of society. They explore the attraction to cults and the tactics used to manipulate individuals. The conversation also touches on the different types of cults and the levels of control they exert over their members.
